- **The Before**: Standard algorithms (QuickSort, MergeSort, HeapSort) used separately.
- **The After**: QuickMergeSort - Uses QuickSort for large partitions, switches to MergeSort for small ones.
- **Big O**: O(n log n)
- **Benchmark**: O(n log n), No memory leaks detected., Stable up to 10^7 records. Elbow at 10^8.

